Package com.gmail.yuyang226.flickr.places

Class Summary
Location A Flickr place.
As a result to PlacesInterface.getInfo(String, String) a Location describes the relation of a place to various types of other places.
Place Describes a place inside a Location.
PlacesInterface Lookup Flickr Places.
PlacesList Simple Extension of SearchResultList.
PlaceType PlaceType as requested by PlacesInterface.getPlaceTypes()
